1
00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:01,310
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:01,310 --> 00:00:02,340
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:02,340 --> 00:00:03,340
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:04,640 --> 00:00:06,540
(Additional painting for the CEO,
and also payment to Park Cheol Su)

5
00:00:06,610 --> 00:00:07,750
(Episode 72)

6
00:00:09,550 --> 00:00:11,120
(Additional painting for the CEO,
and also payment to Park Cheol Su)

7
00:00:12,880 --> 00:00:15,690
He's the guy Park Tae Ho used
during his takeover of Temi Bio.

8
00:00:16,620 --> 00:00:18,920
I'll tell you
what he did in due time.

9
00:00:19,260 --> 00:00:20,330
For now, just find him.

10
00:00:20,730 --> 00:00:22,660
He's extremely secretive,

11
00:00:23,190 --> 00:00:25,530
so I'm not sure
if that number still works.

12
00:00:26,200 --> 00:00:27,700
You said
your father was resourceful.

13
00:00:28,630 --> 00:00:29,800
Have him look for him.

14
00:00:29,800 --> 00:00:32,140
Yes, I'll find him no matter what.

15
00:00:32,970 --> 00:00:33,970
I won't fail.

16
00:00:35,740 --> 00:00:38,440
Good. I really like that attitude.

17
00:00:39,040 --> 00:00:42,080
Once we find that man,
we'll have Park Tae Ho on a leash.

18
00:00:42,780 --> 00:00:45,350
Hyun Jun will take over Adele,

19
00:00:45,780 --> 00:00:49,890
and we can also chew up
and spit out Kim Myung Hui.

20
00:01:03,500 --> 00:01:06,440
Right, I knew you'd come.

21
00:01:07,470 --> 00:01:09,210
Are you unhappy
that I'm out like this?

22
00:01:10,010 --> 00:01:11,240
Are you here to pick a fight?

23
00:01:11,810 --> 00:01:12,810
Mrs. Ok.

24
00:01:13,550 --> 00:01:14,550
What the...

25
00:01:14,610 --> 00:01:15,950
What's this?

26
00:01:16,280 --> 00:01:18,180
Did you think
leaving the basement meant...

27
00:01:18,820 --> 00:01:20,520
you were
the lady of this house again?

28
00:01:21,020 --> 00:01:22,050
Don't be mistaken.

29
00:01:22,520 --> 00:01:25,890
From now on,
you're a maid in this house.

30
00:01:26,860 --> 00:01:28,930
What, a maid?

31
00:01:30,600 --> 00:01:33,030
How dare you call me a maid?

32
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:35,530
If you don't obey,

33
00:01:35,970 --> 00:01:39,140
you'll really have to go
on a trip somewhere.

34
00:01:40,440 --> 00:01:41,910
If the chairman makes up his mind,

35
00:01:42,670 --> 00:01:44,880
it'll be a one-way trip, right?

36
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:47,610
If you want to live,

37
00:01:48,450 --> 00:01:49,750
do as you're told.

38
00:01:58,890 --> 00:02:03,660
You start tomorrow at 5 a.m.
Don't be late.

39
00:02:04,060 --> 00:02:05,400
Understood, Oh Jung Ran?

40
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:08,930
What the... Did you just talk to me
like we're equals?

41
00:02:09,330 --> 00:02:10,340
Hey!

42
00:02:11,170 --> 00:02:15,540
From now on, show me proper respect.

43
00:02:17,440 --> 00:02:19,640
- Why that...
- Mother, please.

44
00:02:19,710 --> 00:02:21,080
Let me go.

45
00:02:21,350 --> 00:02:24,850
Mother, there's no use
in fighting right now.

46
00:02:25,220 --> 00:02:28,250
You barely got out of the basement.
We need to wait for our chance.

47
00:02:29,220 --> 00:02:32,660
Just be patient
until I find Park Cheol Su.

48
00:02:34,790 --> 00:02:35,790
Darn it.

49
00:02:39,300 --> 00:02:40,300
(Additional painting for the CEO,
and also payment to Park Cheol Su)

50
00:02:46,340 --> 00:02:48,740
What is this? Why are you even here?

51
00:02:50,640 --> 00:02:52,040
I have something
to talk to you about.

52
00:02:54,910 --> 00:02:57,080
I don't think
we have anything to discuss.

53
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:58,550
Right.

54
00:02:59,050 --> 00:03:01,550
Well, that's about to change.

55
00:03:05,490 --> 00:03:08,890
I hold your life in my hands,
you see.

56
00:03:10,060 --> 00:03:11,060
What?

57
00:03:19,740 --> 00:03:20,770
(Subject 1: Park Hyun Jun,
Subject 2: Song Geun Tae)

58
00:03:22,110 --> 00:03:23,410
(Test Results)

59
00:03:23,470 --> 00:03:25,080
(The results are indicative
of a paternal relationship.)

60
00:03:34,890 --> 00:03:37,690
Oh Jung Ran may be
out of the basement,

61
00:03:38,260 --> 00:03:41,390
but she is no longer your wife
or the lady of the Adele Group.

62
00:03:41,760 --> 00:03:43,390
She can't live like she used to.

63
00:03:44,500 --> 00:03:47,330
I'm thinking of making her
work under Butler Ok.

64
00:03:49,370 --> 00:03:51,300
That's not enough to satisfy me.

65
00:03:52,170 --> 00:03:55,510
I should just drag her out
and finish her off.

66
00:03:58,540 --> 00:04:00,810
You! Come here.

67
00:04:01,880 --> 00:04:02,880
Yes?

68
00:04:06,420 --> 00:04:09,420
I saw you bring
Oh Jung Ran in earlier.

69
00:04:10,150 --> 00:04:11,160
What happened?

70
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:13,990
It seemed like the police
were looking for her,

71
00:04:14,060 --> 00:04:15,190
so I acted preemptively.

72
00:04:15,590 --> 00:04:16,590
And the basement door?

73
00:04:16,690 --> 00:04:19,400
I explained the situation
to Mrs. Ok, and she opened it.

74
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:22,230
You weren't conspiring
with Oh Jung Ran...

75
00:04:22,530 --> 00:04:25,500
after Driver Song got out
and reported her missing?

76
00:04:27,210 --> 00:04:31,110
I'd rather be in your good graces
than hers, sir.

77
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:33,340
That way, Hyun Jun
will be acknowledged...

78
00:04:33,410 --> 00:04:34,850
and our joint venture will succeed.

79
00:04:35,110 --> 00:04:38,650
Why would I go out of my way
to anger you?

80
00:04:40,280 --> 00:04:42,850
If you want to be
in the chairman's good graces that badly,

81
00:04:43,660 --> 00:04:46,120
don't take matters into your own hands
like you did today.

82
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:50,830
I guess nothing I do
is good enough for you, Ms. Kim.

83
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:06,840
- You got this from Oh Jung Ran?
- Yes.

84
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:10,650
If we find this person,

85
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:13,050
he could testify about the incident
from seven years ago.

86
00:05:14,050 --> 00:05:17,590
Yes. I'll contact James
and get on it.

87
00:05:17,790 --> 00:05:20,930
Okay, and let me know
if you need my help.

88
00:05:50,520 --> 00:05:53,120
What kind of sick game
are you playing?

89
00:05:53,730 --> 00:05:55,030
What do you mean it's a game?

90
00:05:55,930 --> 00:05:57,100
I'm dead serious.

91
00:05:57,160 --> 00:06:00,700
The fact that
you're not Chairman Park's son...

92
00:06:00,770 --> 00:06:02,100
but Driver Song's son...

93
00:06:02,870 --> 00:06:06,940
I have a lot to take care of
with this information.

94
00:06:07,770 --> 00:06:10,710
It's not just your life on the line,
but mine too.

95
00:06:13,110 --> 00:06:14,110
No.

96
00:06:15,180 --> 00:06:17,820
No way. How is that possible?

97
00:06:19,550 --> 00:06:21,750
How could I be... It's not true!

98
00:06:24,290 --> 00:06:25,920
Choi Yu Na,
how can I believe a word you say?

99
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,430
This has to be a mistake.

100
00:06:30,700 --> 00:06:33,870
Fine. I guess you need
to confirm it for yourself.

101
00:06:35,030 --> 00:06:36,830
Either get another DNA test
with Driver Song,

102
00:06:36,830 --> 00:06:38,270
or confront your mother,

103
00:06:39,100 --> 00:06:41,470
but make it quick. You see,

104
00:06:42,340 --> 00:06:45,010
I'm a little pressed for time.

105
00:06:55,450 --> 00:06:57,290
It might be fate that your secret...

106
00:06:58,390 --> 00:06:59,760
fell into my hands.

107
00:07:00,730 --> 00:07:03,930
You deserve to suffer just as much.

108
00:07:03,930 --> 00:07:06,930
You're also responsible
for what happened...

109
00:07:07,830 --> 00:07:09,000
seven years ago.

110
00:07:10,430 --> 00:07:11,500
Seven years ago,

111
00:07:13,500 --> 00:07:16,770
you stole Baek Jin Ju's design.
I reported it, too.

112
00:07:17,410 --> 00:07:18,410
Well,

113
00:07:20,340 --> 00:07:22,710
I reported it
on Baek Jin Ju's behalf.

114
00:07:23,180 --> 00:07:25,180
You're the one who reported it,

115
00:07:26,380 --> 00:07:27,390
not Baek Jin Ju?

116
00:07:30,390 --> 00:07:32,090
If you hadn't interfered,

117
00:07:33,460 --> 00:07:35,190
I might've made a different choice.

118
00:07:36,160 --> 00:07:38,160
Even if that accident happened
seven years ago,

119
00:07:39,660 --> 00:07:41,870
I could be living a completely
different life right now.

120
00:07:44,200 --> 00:07:46,540
You brought this on yourself,
Park Hyun Jun.

121
00:07:48,540 --> 00:07:50,240
And I'm going to protect the life...

122
00:07:51,440 --> 00:07:52,440
you tried to ruin.

123
00:08:05,060 --> 00:08:06,090
Seriously?

124
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:12,600
Hyun Jun.

125
00:08:18,870 --> 00:08:20,040
Hyun Jun.

126
00:08:21,440 --> 00:08:23,540
What brings you here at this hour?

127
00:08:25,340 --> 00:08:26,340
Goodness.

128
00:08:26,880 --> 00:08:30,250
You're so pale. Are you sick?

129
00:08:30,510 --> 00:08:32,350
Should I call a doctor
or an ambulance?

130
00:08:32,350 --> 00:08:34,150
Maybe I should get some medicine.

131
00:08:34,690 --> 00:08:35,690
Mr. Song.

132
00:08:35,920 --> 00:08:36,920
Yes?

133
00:08:37,490 --> 00:08:40,890
- Are you worried about me?
- Of course I am!

134
00:08:40,930 --> 00:08:41,930
Why?

135
00:08:43,760 --> 00:08:45,230
What do you mean, "of course?"

136
00:08:45,460 --> 00:08:46,500
What?

137
00:08:53,500 --> 00:08:55,310
You're nothing but the driver,

138
00:08:56,310 --> 00:08:58,880
so why do you act like
it's your job to worry about me?

139
00:09:00,780 --> 00:09:02,410
Hyun Jun...

140
00:09:04,220 --> 00:09:06,020
Because...

141
00:09:06,920 --> 00:09:09,050
of the way you overreact,

142
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:12,660
people say absurd things,

143
00:09:14,030 --> 00:09:16,090
like I'm your son.

144
00:09:17,730 --> 00:09:18,730
What?

145
00:09:20,300 --> 00:09:21,830
Tell me this isn't true.

146
00:09:22,100 --> 00:09:23,500
"What a load of crap."

147
00:09:23,500 --> 00:09:26,170
"You're definitely not my son.
Your father is Chairman Park."

148
00:09:26,170 --> 00:09:27,570
Just say it already!

149
00:09:28,140 --> 00:09:29,840
Hyun Jun, you're...

150
00:09:33,210 --> 00:09:34,210
You're...

151
00:09:43,490 --> 00:09:46,020
What am I supposed to think
when you look at me like that?

152
00:09:47,020 --> 00:09:50,860
If you can't even say it's not true,
what am I supposed to do?

153
00:09:52,330 --> 00:09:53,560
I'm the son...

154
00:09:54,670 --> 00:09:56,730
of the Adele Group's
Chairman Park Tae Ho.

155
00:10:00,040 --> 00:10:03,470
How could someone like you... How?

156
00:10:04,310 --> 00:10:08,050
How can I be your son? How?

157
00:10:11,320 --> 00:10:12,920
Hyun Jun, wait!

158
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:16,020
Hyun Jun...

159
00:10:19,020 --> 00:10:21,490
How on earth did he find out?

160
00:10:23,290 --> 00:10:24,530
My Hyun Jun.

161
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:28,870
He doesn't deserve
to have his heart broken.

162
00:10:31,570 --> 00:10:33,400
Because of someone like me...

163
00:10:34,140 --> 00:10:36,040
Because of someone like me,

164
00:10:36,870 --> 00:10:39,780
he shouldn't have
to suffer like that.

165
00:10:40,040 --> 00:10:43,050
Hyun Jun, what do I do?

166
00:10:43,510 --> 00:10:46,280
Hyun Jun...

167
00:10:59,900 --> 00:11:00,930
If they find out...

168
00:11:03,300 --> 00:11:05,740
What happens if everyone finds out?

169
00:11:08,640 --> 00:11:10,040
What if Min Jun...

170
00:11:13,310 --> 00:11:15,010
and Jin Ju find out too?

171
00:11:18,220 --> 00:11:19,280
No.

172
00:11:21,720 --> 00:11:22,790
No.

173
00:11:23,350 --> 00:11:25,560
How did the police get involved?

174
00:11:26,160 --> 00:11:29,560
I bet it was that jerk Driver Song
who called it in.

175
00:11:29,660 --> 00:11:32,630
They said the caller wished
to remain anonymous.

176
00:11:33,160 --> 00:11:36,370
Based on the circumstances,
it appears to be Driver Song.

177
00:11:37,940 --> 00:11:40,840
Just as I suspected, Oh Jung Ran
stabbed me in the back again.

178
00:11:41,110 --> 00:11:43,740
Find that darn Driver Song
and bring him to me now.

179
00:11:44,640 --> 00:11:48,410
Lock him in the basement again,
so he can't report anything else.

180
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:51,550
No. Make sure he never sees
the light of day again!

181
00:11:51,620 --> 00:11:52,920
Yes, sir.

182
00:11:53,350 --> 00:11:54,350
And...

183
00:11:55,790 --> 00:11:57,020
tell me about Chloe.

184
00:11:57,020 --> 00:11:58,920
Has anything suspicious happened...

185
00:11:59,360 --> 00:12:00,890
since she moved in?

186
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:05,460
No, sir.

187
00:12:07,060 --> 00:12:10,230
I suspect she's working
with Oh Jung Ran,

188
00:12:10,630 --> 00:12:12,070
so whether she's at home or out,

189
00:12:12,700 --> 00:12:14,910
don't take your eyes off her.

190
00:12:15,010 --> 00:12:16,010
Yes, sir.

191
00:12:39,800 --> 00:12:42,370
What's going on?
He should've at least called.

192
00:12:43,800 --> 00:12:45,470
Did something happen to him?

193
00:12:59,350 --> 00:13:00,780
(Chloe)

194
00:13:05,320 --> 00:13:08,130
I'm supposed to let you use me.

195
00:13:11,130 --> 00:13:13,930
That's the only way
I can stay by your side.

196
00:13:17,700 --> 00:13:20,300
If I'm not Park Tae Ho's son...

197
00:13:21,610 --> 00:13:24,340
and I become useless to you,

198
00:13:29,180 --> 00:13:31,350
you'll leave me, won't you?

199
00:13:35,490 --> 00:13:37,520
Will you go back to Min Jun?

200
00:13:43,330 --> 00:13:44,800
And just like that,

201
00:13:50,070 --> 00:13:52,140
am I going to be abandoned?

202
00:14:40,480 --> 00:14:41,650
I'm sorry...

203
00:14:44,120 --> 00:14:45,460
that I couldn't...

204
00:14:48,360 --> 00:14:49,830
be more.

205
00:14:53,200 --> 00:14:55,030
I'm not successful...

206
00:14:56,570 --> 00:14:58,370
or talented,

207
00:14:59,570 --> 00:15:01,310
and I'm sorry, Hyun Jun.

208
00:15:04,440 --> 00:15:06,110
Dad is...

209
00:15:09,110 --> 00:15:10,380
so sorry.

210
00:15:42,650 --> 00:15:43,810
Wait.

211
00:15:47,990 --> 00:15:50,420
Did something happen to Hyun Jun?

212
00:15:50,790 --> 00:15:51,790
Why?

213
00:15:52,560 --> 00:15:55,430
He didn't come home,
and I can't reach him.

214
00:15:59,430 --> 00:16:01,300
I'm sorry. I shouldn't have asked.

215
00:16:02,430 --> 00:16:03,900
I'll find out where he is.

216
00:16:05,900 --> 00:16:06,900
I'll...

217
00:16:07,710 --> 00:16:08,740
check on him too.

218
00:16:44,270 --> 00:16:45,280
What's wrong with you?

219
00:16:45,810 --> 00:16:49,880
You disappeared on Jin Ju
and spent the whole night drinking?

220
00:16:49,950 --> 00:16:53,050
Did you marry her
just to make her worry?

221
00:16:54,080 --> 00:16:57,890
If you can't protect her,
then end this ridiculous marriage.

222
00:16:57,920 --> 00:17:02,090
I can protect her just fine.

223
00:17:11,030 --> 00:17:12,040
Park Min Jun.

224
00:17:14,710 --> 00:17:15,910
I will never...

225
00:17:17,710 --> 00:17:19,240
lose her to you.

226
00:17:20,580 --> 00:17:22,150
Then get your act together.

227
00:17:22,880 --> 00:17:26,380
I didn't give up on Jin Ju.
For her sake,

228
00:17:27,180 --> 00:17:29,690
I'm just barely holding myself back.

229
00:18:00,750 --> 00:18:01,990
Looks like you've confirmed it.

230
00:18:05,820 --> 00:18:09,230
I never thought I'd see
Park Hyun Jun look so pathetic.

231
00:18:09,230 --> 00:18:10,260
Hold on.

232
00:18:10,660 --> 00:18:12,560
Is it finally showing...

233
00:18:12,900 --> 00:18:15,770
that you're Driver Song's son,
not Chairman Park's?

234
00:18:16,030 --> 00:18:17,030
Just...

235
00:18:17,370 --> 00:18:18,700
shut it.

236
00:18:22,410 --> 00:18:25,510
Right. I guess
we're not close enough...

237
00:18:25,710 --> 00:18:27,850
to worry about each other.

238
00:18:32,850 --> 00:18:34,250
What do you want?

239
00:18:35,620 --> 00:18:38,290
What are you trying to do
by holding my secret over my head?

240
00:18:39,820 --> 00:18:40,920
For starters...

241
00:18:44,390 --> 00:18:46,030
We need to solve this problem.

242
00:18:46,460 --> 00:18:47,560
At Min Jun's instruction,

243
00:18:47,560 --> 00:18:49,930
the legal team sent over
this notice.

244
00:18:50,270 --> 00:18:52,740
If you want to keep living
as Chairman Park's son,

245
00:18:54,240 --> 00:18:55,240
deal with it.

246
00:18:55,740 --> 00:18:57,770
You're still Chairman Park's son
for now.

247
00:18:57,980 --> 00:18:59,710
This much shouldn't be
a problem for you.

248
00:19:01,450 --> 00:19:02,450
You'll use my secret...

249
00:19:03,480 --> 00:19:04,750
to order me around?

250
00:19:06,480 --> 00:19:07,480
Fine.

251
00:19:11,260 --> 00:19:12,290
I'll play along.

252
00:19:14,760 --> 00:19:17,090
But you'd better tell me straight.

253
00:19:17,930 --> 00:19:21,230
Where and how did you find this out?
Who else knows besides you?

254
00:19:25,300 --> 00:19:27,910
I was suspicious
of Ms. Oh and Driver Song,

255
00:19:27,910 --> 00:19:29,310
so I requested a DNA test.

256
00:19:30,340 --> 00:19:33,080
I'm the only one
who knows your secret,

257
00:19:33,940 --> 00:19:36,180
so you just do as I say.

258
00:19:39,750 --> 00:19:41,550
You'd better be telling the truth.

259
00:19:42,650 --> 00:19:44,220
If this secret gets out,

260
00:19:46,820 --> 00:19:48,530
I'll make you pay.

261
00:20:20,320 --> 00:20:22,160
Who else knows this secret?

262
00:20:24,090 --> 00:20:26,130
If he finds out
President Kim already knows,

263
00:20:26,460 --> 00:20:28,230
I'll lose my leverage.

264
00:20:29,900 --> 00:20:32,770
Until President Kim
reveals this secret herself,

265
00:20:34,340 --> 00:20:36,140
I have to use Park Hyun Jun...

266
00:20:37,540 --> 00:20:39,210
to go up against Min Jun.

267
00:20:43,010 --> 00:20:45,320
Hello,
is this the real estate agency?

268
00:20:46,480 --> 00:20:50,650
Right. We'd like to list our house.

269
00:20:50,720 --> 00:20:52,920
Hurry up
and ask about the market price.

270
00:20:53,090 --> 00:20:57,190
All right. Could you give me
the current market price?

271
00:20:57,660 --> 00:20:59,760
Yes, the address is...

272
00:21:00,060 --> 00:21:01,670
- It's...
- My goodness.

273
00:21:02,500 --> 00:21:06,240
- What do you think you're doing?
- I could ask you the same thing.

274
00:21:06,300 --> 00:21:09,010
Isn't it obvious?
We're cleaning up your mess.

275
00:21:09,810 --> 00:21:12,240
I consulted a lawyer,

276
00:21:12,340 --> 00:21:14,310
and they said we'll lose
if this goes to court.

277
00:21:14,510 --> 00:21:18,850
We have to settle before they sue us
to avoid fraud charges.

278
00:21:18,920 --> 00:21:21,920
Exactly. Now, give that back.

279
00:21:22,050 --> 00:21:25,060
We have to list the house
right away.

280
00:21:26,190 --> 00:21:28,360
- There's no need for that.
- What?

281
00:21:28,630 --> 00:21:30,560
It'll all be taken care of soon.

282
00:21:30,630 --> 00:21:33,160
It'll be resolved? How?

283
00:21:33,430 --> 00:21:37,170
Seriously,
what are you planning to do now?

284
00:21:37,700 --> 00:21:39,840
Just stay out of it, will you?

285
00:21:39,940 --> 00:21:42,010
I'm telling you,
stop making such a mess.

286
00:21:42,010 --> 00:21:43,710
This time is different.

287
00:21:44,040 --> 00:21:47,640
It's guaranteed to work,
so just trust me and wait.

288
00:21:49,580 --> 00:21:50,580
Really?

289
00:21:54,180 --> 00:21:56,890
Come on, seriously. Darn it.

290
00:21:57,090 --> 00:21:58,120
Unbelievable.

291
00:21:58,590 --> 00:22:01,730
Oh Jung Ran,
what time do you think it is?

292
00:22:01,860 --> 00:22:05,930
We were supposed to start at 5 a.m.,
and now it's noon.

293
00:22:05,930 --> 00:22:08,530
Did you really think
I'd just obey you?

294
00:22:09,330 --> 00:22:10,330
Right.

295
00:22:11,570 --> 00:22:14,470
She's not the type to just do
as she's told.

296
00:22:15,040 --> 00:22:17,870
Secretary Jung,
bring the ingredients we prepared.

297
00:22:17,940 --> 00:22:19,640
Yes, ma'am.

298
00:22:21,950 --> 00:22:23,450
What's all this?

299
00:22:23,580 --> 00:22:25,950
You should be able to guess
from the ingredients.

300
00:22:25,980 --> 00:22:27,880
Have you forgotten your days
as a maid?

301
00:22:27,920 --> 00:22:29,190
Seriously?

302
00:22:29,750 --> 00:22:31,590
Who do you think you are,
talking to me like that?

303
00:22:31,660 --> 00:22:33,920
You're a maid now,
not the chairman's wife.

304
00:22:34,060 --> 00:22:37,430
We can drop the formalities,
can't we?

305
00:22:39,200 --> 00:22:40,900
You're the one
who needs to watch their mouth.

306
00:22:44,230 --> 00:22:47,300
So, what am I supposed to do
with all this?

307
00:22:47,670 --> 00:22:49,610
These are all the ingredients
for dumplings.

308
00:22:50,040 --> 00:22:53,610
You've got two hands,
so make them yourself.

309
00:22:53,680 --> 00:22:55,050
Are you kidding me?

310
00:22:55,110 --> 00:22:58,010
If you don't like it,
you can go back to the basement.

311
00:22:58,850 --> 00:23:01,850
Fine. You want to see who wins this?

312
00:23:01,850 --> 00:23:04,050
Then go ahead. Try and win.

313
00:23:04,490 --> 00:23:07,390
Mrs. Ok, don't you dare help her.

314
00:23:07,390 --> 00:23:09,460
Yes, understood.

315
00:23:14,160 --> 00:23:15,170
Darn it.

316
00:23:17,530 --> 00:23:21,200
Oh Jung Ran, start with the filling.

317
00:23:29,810 --> 00:23:31,880
If you throw this away too,

318
00:23:31,950 --> 00:23:34,920
you'll have to redo
all the prep work.

319
00:23:36,520 --> 00:23:37,750
Why you...

320
00:23:42,930 --> 00:23:44,190
Darn it.

321
00:23:48,370 --> 00:23:49,700
Enjoy your coffee.

322
00:23:49,770 --> 00:23:51,570
(Bongmyeong Neighborhood Coffee)

323
00:23:57,570 --> 00:24:00,780
Boss, aren't you going to put him
in his place today?

324
00:24:01,680 --> 00:24:02,680
Put him in his place?

325
00:24:02,750 --> 00:24:05,050
What... What are you talking about?

326
00:24:05,380 --> 00:24:06,980
When did I ever do that?

327
00:24:07,050 --> 00:24:10,550
You did when he and your sister
were flirting.

328
00:24:10,690 --> 00:24:12,460
You tried to come between them.

329
00:24:13,660 --> 00:24:14,760
Flirting?

330
00:24:16,430 --> 00:24:20,360
It's not that. Flirting, my gosh.
Young lady, come on.

331
00:24:20,430 --> 00:24:22,700
Exactly. What flirting?

332
00:24:23,870 --> 00:24:25,500
Gosh, look at the time.

333
00:24:25,570 --> 00:24:27,270
Na Yeon, you should head home now.

334
00:24:27,340 --> 00:24:30,870
Part-timers should leave on time.
Go on now. Bye.

335
00:24:33,580 --> 00:24:35,550
Don't pay any attention to her.

336
00:24:36,910 --> 00:24:38,950
There's nothing to worry about.

337
00:24:39,050 --> 00:24:40,550
Right. Whatever.

338
00:24:42,190 --> 00:24:44,720
Anyway, where are you
with Park Cheol Su?

339
00:24:44,720 --> 00:24:45,720
Did you find him?

340
00:24:45,720 --> 00:24:49,490
The owner of that number,
Park Cheol Su, is dead.

341
00:24:49,990 --> 00:24:51,460
It seems
he was using a burner phone.

342
00:24:52,230 --> 00:24:54,330
So we'll never find him?

343
00:24:55,500 --> 00:24:59,200
I was told
Park Cheol Su handles explosives.

344
00:24:59,540 --> 00:25:02,610
Then he'll need to get materials
to make them.

345
00:25:03,170 --> 00:25:05,510
Is there any way
we can look into that?

346
00:25:08,950 --> 00:25:10,010
Perhaps.

347
00:25:10,010 --> 00:25:11,050
What?

348
00:25:11,650 --> 00:25:13,120
Do you know something about that?

349
00:25:13,650 --> 00:25:14,820
Eunhwa Trading.

350
00:25:15,250 --> 00:25:17,690
They're the ones who introduced
Park Cheol Su to Chairman Park.

351
00:25:18,360 --> 00:25:21,360
I heard they can get anything,
whether it's an object or a person.

352
00:25:21,990 --> 00:25:24,090
Could we try contacting them?

353
00:25:24,090 --> 00:25:26,800
I think we should discuss that
with Dan Hui first.

354
00:25:26,900 --> 00:25:28,930
How about we all meet
at my place and talk?

355
00:25:29,230 --> 00:25:32,400
Yes, of course.
That sounds like a good idea.

356
00:25:32,540 --> 00:25:35,670
I'll talk to Ms. Kim
and arrange a time.

357
00:25:45,250 --> 00:25:48,420
This is a legal notice
sent to Ms. Choi...

358
00:25:49,220 --> 00:25:51,290
from the legal team. Tell them...

359
00:25:53,920 --> 00:25:55,360
Tell them...

360
00:25:56,190 --> 00:25:58,360
I ordered all proceedings
to be halted.

361
00:25:58,460 --> 00:26:00,230
But...

362
00:26:00,730 --> 00:26:04,170
I believed this came directly
from the vice president.

363
00:26:05,070 --> 00:26:06,070
Manager So.

364
00:26:07,870 --> 00:26:09,840
Are you going to follow
Park Min Jun's orders...

365
00:26:10,910 --> 00:26:12,780
and ignore mine?

366
00:26:13,080 --> 00:26:15,310
No, that's not what I meant.

367
00:26:15,310 --> 00:26:17,710
Then go and tell them.

368
00:26:19,750 --> 00:26:21,580
I'll deal with Park Min Jun myself.

369
00:26:35,500 --> 00:26:38,030
Just go and tell them!

370
00:26:45,210 --> 00:26:46,840
What on earth happened?

371
00:26:47,640 --> 00:26:49,080
Something's wrong, isn't it?

372
00:26:54,320 --> 00:26:55,450
Well...

373
00:27:06,500 --> 00:27:07,500
I'm sorry.

374
00:27:12,870 --> 00:27:13,900
I'm sorry.

375
00:27:15,440 --> 00:27:17,010
I met up with some friends...

376
00:27:18,240 --> 00:27:19,840
to celebrate my wedding,

377
00:27:21,810 --> 00:27:23,310
and I drank way too much.

378
00:27:25,320 --> 00:27:26,380
I'm sorry.

379
00:27:27,450 --> 00:27:28,450
Sorry.

380
00:27:37,460 --> 00:27:40,000
Park Hyun Jun gave orders
to the legal team?

381
00:27:40,800 --> 00:27:41,800
Yes.

382
00:27:42,170 --> 00:27:43,700
He ordered them
to halt all proceedings...

383
00:27:43,700 --> 00:27:45,400
related to Ms. Choi's case.

384
00:27:47,140 --> 00:27:48,470
But why?

385
00:27:49,870 --> 00:27:53,980
Hyun Jun has no reason,
to interfere with Choi Yu Na's case.

386
00:27:54,710 --> 00:27:58,580
What should we do?
Should we stop or continue?

387
00:27:59,150 --> 00:28:02,690
Please continue.
I'll go meet with Hyun Jun.

388
00:28:02,750 --> 00:28:03,790
Yes, sir.

389
00:28:04,090 --> 00:28:07,090
(Adele)

390
00:28:14,230 --> 00:28:15,230
Hyun Jun.

391
00:28:16,130 --> 00:28:18,100
Are you sure nothing's wrong?

392
00:28:18,770 --> 00:28:21,940
Yes. Why would anything be wrong?

393
00:28:23,940 --> 00:28:25,880
I just feel bad
for staying out all night...

394
00:28:27,280 --> 00:28:28,880
without telling you first.

395
00:28:31,250 --> 00:28:32,750
It won't happen again.

396
00:28:33,980 --> 00:28:36,920
Okay.
I'm just glad you're all right.

397
00:28:38,320 --> 00:28:40,790
I have to go meet James,

398
00:28:41,420 --> 00:28:42,830
so you head on home.

399
00:28:43,260 --> 00:28:45,100
Okay, sure thing.

400
00:29:18,560 --> 00:29:20,860
I wonder if my Hyun Jun
is all right.

401
00:29:23,930 --> 00:29:26,400
I need to tell Jung Ran about this.

402
00:29:36,010 --> 00:29:37,010
Hyun Jun.

403
00:29:45,220 --> 00:29:46,860
How could someone like you...

404
00:29:47,290 --> 00:29:51,030
How can I be your son? How?

405
00:30:09,580 --> 00:30:12,750
I'm not happy with the shape
of any of these.

406
00:30:14,020 --> 00:30:16,820
If the shape is so important,
tell them to go eat out.

407
00:30:16,820 --> 00:30:19,490
"What looks good, tastes good."

408
00:30:20,520 --> 00:30:24,360
That's what you said, Jung Ran.
Don't you remember?

409
00:30:24,530 --> 00:30:25,530
When did I say that?

410
00:30:26,730 --> 00:30:30,070
Forget the dumplings.
Do the dishes and clean up.

411
00:30:30,300 --> 00:30:32,700
No gloves. Got it?

412
00:30:33,770 --> 00:30:36,810
What? How am I supposed
to wash all this without gloves?

413
00:30:38,680 --> 00:30:41,910
How else will you know
if you got all the grease off?

414
00:30:42,250 --> 00:30:44,750
Wash them until they're squeaky clean,
understand?

415
00:30:45,950 --> 00:30:49,090
That's another thing
you used to say, Jung Ran.

416
00:30:50,050 --> 00:30:51,520
You are really something else.

417
00:30:52,020 --> 00:30:55,120
Then make sure
the dishes are spotless.

418
00:30:57,560 --> 00:31:01,260
Darn it. Unbelievable. I swear...

419
00:31:02,800 --> 00:31:06,200
Just wait until Chloe digs up
some dirt on Park Tae Ho.

420
00:31:06,200 --> 00:31:08,940
Kim Myung Hui and Butler Ok.

421
00:31:09,110 --> 00:31:12,380
I'll make them slave away
making dumplings and kimchi all day.

422
00:31:13,080 --> 00:31:14,080
Darn.

423
00:31:14,440 --> 00:31:15,810
Gosh, Hyun Jun.

424
00:31:16,680 --> 00:31:19,480
Son, couldn't you have
come home sooner?

425
00:31:19,880 --> 00:31:22,350
Kim Myung Hui and Butler Ok
have been driving me insane.

426
00:31:23,190 --> 00:31:25,690
Chloe finally managed to get me
out of the basement,

427
00:31:25,990 --> 00:31:28,360
but they're treating me
like a maid and...

428
00:31:28,760 --> 00:31:31,690
Hyun Jun, that hurts.
What's wrong with you?

429
00:31:34,030 --> 00:31:36,770
Hold on. That hurts!

430
00:31:40,040 --> 00:31:41,040
Hyun Jun.

431
00:31:41,070 --> 00:31:42,810
What's gotten into you
all of a sudden?

432
00:31:44,040 --> 00:31:46,580
Were you upset
seeing your mom treated like a maid?

433
00:31:47,310 --> 00:31:49,610
I'm just putting up with it for now.

434
00:31:50,210 --> 00:31:52,020
When Chloe finds dirt
on your father...

435
00:31:52,020 --> 00:31:53,020
My father?

436
00:31:54,250 --> 00:31:55,420
And who exactly is that?

437
00:31:58,760 --> 00:32:01,990
It's Park Tae Ho, of course.

438
00:32:02,930 --> 00:32:03,990
Why? What's wrong?

439
00:32:06,230 --> 00:32:07,230
Tell me the truth.

440
00:32:09,130 --> 00:32:10,900
Is Chairman Park Tae Ho really...

441
00:32:12,840 --> 00:32:13,840
my father?

442
00:32:16,840 --> 00:32:18,140
Whose son am I?

443
00:32:20,480 --> 00:32:22,550
Tell me who my father is!

444
00:32:52,580 --> 00:32:55,580
(Pearl in Red)

445
00:32:55,580 --> 00:32:57,080
Who are you to worry about me?

446
00:32:57,350 --> 00:32:59,750
Are you showing up now to claim me
as your son and take all the credit?

447
00:32:59,850 --> 00:33:00,920
Of course not.

448
00:33:01,020 --> 00:33:04,620
Then don't ever show your face
in front of me again,

449
00:33:04,620 --> 00:33:06,920
because
I'm Chairman Park Tae Ho's son.

450
00:33:06,920 --> 00:33:08,390
What do you think you're doing?

451
00:33:08,990 --> 00:33:12,460
You dared to break Hyun Jun's heart?

452
00:33:12,600 --> 00:33:15,030
I may have nothing,
and I may be powerless,

453
00:33:15,630 --> 00:33:17,500
but I won't just stand by
and let you hurt my child.

454
00:33:17,600 --> 00:33:19,100
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
